screen_desc:
A screenshot of a ride-hailing app interface titled "Plan your ride." The pickup location is set to "Washington Hilton," and the destination is "Virginia Hospital Center." Below the destination input, there are several location suggestions, including:

1. Virginia Hospital Center, 1701 N George Mason Dr, Arlington, VA
2. Virginia Hospital Center Emergency Room, 1701 N George Mason Dr, Arlington, VA
3. VHC Health-Virginia Hospital Center, 1701 N George Mason Dr, Arlington, VA
4. The Virginia Hospital Center, 764 S 23rd St, Arlington, VA
5. VHC Health Outpatient Pavilion, 1851 N George Mason Dr, Arlington, VA

Additional options include "Search in a different city," "Get more results for VHC Health - Virginia Hospital Center," and "Set location on map." The time displayed on the phone is 3:08 PM, and the status bar shows various icons, including battery, signal strength, and notifications.
